---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { meta } from "../data";
---

<Base title={meta.artifacts.title} description={meta.artifacts.description} canonical="/artifacts/">
  <section>
    <h1>Artifacts</h1>
    <div class="artifact-list">
      <div class="artifact-entry">
        <h3>Cash flow report from bank exports.</h3>
        <p>Multi-bank, multi-currency cash reporting built directly from bank statements: opening and closing cash by account, inflows, outflows, internal transfers, weekly and monthly views, flagged transactions. Built for two real companies with no finance system in place.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="artifact-entry">
        <h3>Cap table scenario model.</h3>
        <p>Round-by-round ownership modeling: option pool timing, convertible conversion, anti-dilution scenarios, down round mechanics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="artifact-entry">
        <h3>Diligence readiness checklist.</h3>
        <p>The questions a diligence process will ask, organized by the five sections of this library.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>Each artifact comes from work with a real company. They are shared, not sold.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
